      <p>The statistics presented here describe a small <a href="ch73s21.html#MonstersAnimals68">horse</a>, under 5 feet tall at the shoulder. <a href="ch73s33.html#MonstersAnimals122">Ponies</a> are otherwise similar to light <a href="ch73s21.html#MonstersAnimals68">horses</a> and cannot fight while carrying a rider.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2306123"/>Combat</h5>
