        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals123"/>
        <p>*A <a href="ch73s33.html#MonstersAnimals122">pony</a> not trained for war does not normally use its hooves to attack but rather to run. Its hoof attack is treated as a secondary attack and adds only half the <a href="ch73s33.html#MonstersAnimals122">pony's</a> Strength bonus to damage.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2306164"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals124"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Carrying Capacity:</strong></span> A light load for a <a href="ch73s33.html#MonstersAnimals122">pony</a> is up to 75 pounds; a medium load, 76-150 pounds; and a heavy load, 151-225 pounds. A <a href="ch73s33.html#MonstersAnimals122">pony</a> can drag 1,125 pounds.</p>
